This Project is for Hibernate

A)Hibernate

a)Maven

1)Project Management Tool.
2)To manage dependencies.
3)Hibernate core dependency.

b)Entity(Class)

1)Class is like Table and properties are columns.
2)Annotations to declare, @Entity, @Id(Primary key), @Table.

c)Main Code

1)Hibernate helps in simply using Objects to save data in SQL.
2)Make a Session using SessionFactory and Session Classes.
3)To fulfill ACID properties use Transaction Class.